name: Begonia Maculata
description:
Begonia Maculata also known as Polka Dot Begonia, Trout Begonia, Spotted begonia, is a lovely plant belonging to the family Begoniaceae.

Maculata is an easy-to-care-for houseplant, It loves indirect light and can grow 3ft.
Its leaves are a deep green color with bright white and somewhat uniform spots, also underneath the color is pink mixed with red,burgundy.
